data.description: This property has amazing potential as an investment or development. The house has a new roof and new sub-flooring. It's just waiting for someone to finish the renovation. The home is very spacious and there is a bonus room that has been a non-conforming bedroom in addition to two other bedrooms.  The parcel is over 5 acres of unrestricted land with frontage on Highway 103 W in Hudson! The property also has a creek running through it and is partially fenced.
